## Introduction @unplugged

You've created a greeting, now let's send it over the top!

## Step 1

The code for a simple greeting is already in the workspace.  
‚≠ê Personalize this card by editing the images ‚≠ê

---

üî≤ Choose a background from **My Assets** by clicking on the grey box in 
``||scene:set background image to [ ]||`` and toggling to the **My Assets** tab
(or stay in the **Editor** and create your own).

üî≤ Choose some sprite text from **My Assets** by clicking on the grey box in 
``||variables:set [mySprite] to sprite [ ] of kind [Player]||`` and 
toggling to the **My Assets** tab
(or stay in the **Editor** and create your own).  

üî≤ Choose a melody by clicking the note in the ``||music:play melody [ ] at tempo [120] (bps)||`` block.
